This works very well:<p>@media screen and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio:0) { 
  select:focus,
  textarea:focus,
  input:focus {
    font-size: 16px;
  }
}<p>It uses a css selector only available on iOS devices and enables a larger font to prevent zoom.<p>[Original concept] <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/a/16255670/209005" rel="nofollow">http://stackoverflow.com/a/16255670/209005</a>
